'''火星微量氣體任務衛星'''（{{Lang|en|'''ExoMars Trace Gas Orbiter'''、'''TGO'''}}）是[[欧洲空间局|欧洲空间局]]和[[俄罗斯航天国家集团|俄罗斯航天国家集团]]合作的[[ExoMars|ExoMars计划]]中的一部分，该卫星将用于探测火星大气中[[甲烷|甲烷]]和其他微量气体的丰度和时间、空间分布<ref>{{Cite web|title=ExoMars 2016 FAQs|url=https://www.esa.int/Science_Exploration/Human_and_Robotic_Exploration/Exploration/ExoMars/ExoMars_2016_FAQs|access-date=2022-03-19|publisher=欧洲空间局|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220319070902/https://www.esa.int/Science_Exploration/Human_and_Robotic_Exploration/Exploration/ExoMars/ExoMars_2016_FAQs|archive-date=2022-03-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年3月14日，该卫星与[[斯基亞帕雷利EDM登陸器|斯基亞帕雷利EDM登陸器]]搭乘俄罗斯[[質子M型運載火箭|质子号运载火箭]]成功升空<ref name=":0">{{Cite journal|title=欧俄合作“火星生物学”计划成功迈出第一步|author=李金钊、李虹琳|url=https://kns.cnki.net/kcms/detail/detail.aspx?FileName=ZGHT201605009&DbName=CJFQ2016|journal=中国航天|year=2016}}</ref>。该卫星还将会在未来负责[[羅莎琳·富蘭克林號|羅莎琳·富蘭克林號]]等两个火星探索车的通信中继任务<ref name="LaunchMoved2020">{{cite press release| url=http://www.esa.int/For_Media/Press_Releases/Second_ExoMars_mission_moves_to_next_launch_opportunity_in_2020| title=Second ExoMars mission moves to next launch opportunity in 2020| publisher=[[ESA|ESA]]| date=2 May 2016| accessdate=2 May 2016| archive-date=2016-05-02| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160502194618/http://www.esa.int/For_Media/Press_Releases/Second_ExoMars_mission_moves_to_next_launch_opportunity_in_2020| dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="LaunchMoved2022">{{cite web|url=https://www.esa.int/Science_Exploration/Human_and_Robotic_Exploration/Exploration/ExoMars/The_way_forward_to_Mars|title=The way forward to Mars|publisher=[[ESA|ESA]]|date=2020-10-01|access-date=2020-10-05|archive-date=2020-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201230000838/http://www.esa.int/Science_Exploration/Human_and_Robotic_Exploration/Exploration/ExoMars/The_way_forward_to_Mars|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

